org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.GRM

Interface CommunicationMedia

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ProcessingResource, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GaCommHost, HwBridge, HwBus, HwMedia, MessageComResource, SaCommHost, SharedDataComResource, SwCommunicationResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommunicationMediaImpl, GaCommHostImpl, HwBridgeImpl, HwBusImpl, HwMediaImpl, MessageComResourceImpl, SaCommHostImpl, SharedDataComResourceImpl, SwCommunicationResourceImpl

    public interface CommunicationMedia
extends ProcessingResource
    A representation of the model object 'Communication Media'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Element Size
    • Base Connector
    • Transm Mode
    • Block T
    • Packet T
    • Capacity
    See Also:
    GRMPackage.getCommunicationMedia()
